title: Kusi
info:
The soundtrack to Orange's demo The Secret Life of Mr. Black from Assembly 1997. The actual module (kusi.it) is untitled and other markings only contain sample names.

Lyrics:
My family.
This is my family.
My wife, my son, my daughter and I.
I am Mrs. Black. My wife is Mr. Black.
I am Mr. Black's husband.
We have two children, a boy and a girl.
The boy's name is John, he's twelve years old.
The girl's name is Mary, she's still quite young.
I am a woman, my wife is a man, he's twelve years old. (9x)
I am daughter and I. My wife, two children, a boy and a girl. (2x)
